{"lemma":"سَطْرُ","slug":"سَطْرُ","root":"س.ط.ر","root_slug":"س-ط-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ط-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19713","n19714","n19719","n19720","n19721"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to write"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to draw lines into, to rule"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَطَرَ (saṭara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"line, row"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"line of writing"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stroke"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Old South Arabian 𐩪𐩷𐩧 (s¹ṭr, “to inscribe; writing, inscription, document, line”) from Classical Syriac ܣܛܰܪ (sṭar, “to cut, to mark, to carve, to write down”) from Akkadian 𒊬 (šaṭārum, “to write, to inscribe, to jot down”). The root س ط ر (s ṭ r) is derived from this borrowing."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19713","headword_ar":"سَطَرَ","root":"sTr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saTorN","text_ar":"سَطْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Msb, K; *) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sT~r","text_ar":"سطّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstTr","text_ar":"استطر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, A, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wrote"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, * A, Msb, K) a writing or book. (M, Msb.) ―         -b2-  [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saTara","text_ar":"سَطَرَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ruled"},{"kind":"text","text":"a book. (See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoTarapN","text_ar":"مِسْطَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)] ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saTara","text_ar":"سَطَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n. as above, (K, TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut"},{"kind":"text","text":"another man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a sword."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saTarahu","text_ar":"سَطَرَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He prostrated him; threw him down prostrate."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n19714","headword_ar":"سطّر","root":"sTr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1. ―         -b2-  Also, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasoTiyrN","text_ar":"تَسْطِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He composed"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) lies, falsehoods, (TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asaATiyr","text_ar":"اَسَاطِير"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. stories having no foundation, &c. (M.) ―         -b3-  Also, [not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tsT~r","text_ar":"تسطّر"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in Gol.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said what was false:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he pretended a false thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sT~r EalayonaA","text_ar":"سطّر عَلَيْنَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He told us"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asaATiyr","text_ar":"اَسَاطِير"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stories having no foundation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"no right tendency"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he told us stories resembling falsehoods:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he embellished stories to us with lies:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he related to us wonderful"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1358},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stories of the ancients."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sT~r fulaAnN fulaAnFA","text_ar":"سطّر فُلَانٌ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one told falsehoods to such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sT~rhu","text_ar":"سطّرهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to form wishes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desires."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","TA","Lth"]},{"entry_id":"n19719","headword_ar":"سَطْرٌ","root":"sTr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Msb, K,) originally an inf. n., [see 1,] (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saTarN","text_ar":"سَطَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A line"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) of a book or writing: (M, A, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a writing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) and (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a line"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"row"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K) of buildings, (S, A,) and of trees, (S, M, A, Msb, K,) &c., (Msb, K,) and [particularly] of palm-trees, and the like, (M,) [and so, app., ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musoTaArN","text_ar":"مُسْطَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.:] pl. (of the former, S, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoTurN","text_ar":"اَسْطُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K) and (of the latter, S)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoTaArN","text_ar":"اَسْطَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, K) [both pls. of pauc.] and (of the former, S, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suTuwrN","text_ar":"سُطُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asaATiyru","text_ar":"اَسَاطِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, S, M, K) is a pl. pl., (S, K,) i. e. pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoTaArN","text_ar":"اَسْطَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba saTorFA mino kitaAbapK","text_ar":"كَتَبَ سَطْرًا مِنْ كِتَابَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wrote a line of writing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (A:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaY saTorFA","text_ar":"بَنَى سَطْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He built a row"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino binaAy^ihi","text_ar":"مِنْ بِنَايِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his building"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (A:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garasa saTorFA","text_ar":"غَرَسَ سَطْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He planted a row"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino wadiy~ihi","text_ar":"مِنْ وَدِيِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his palm-shoots,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young palm-trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-  [Hence the saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AijoEali","text_ar":"اِجْعَلِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amora saTorFA waAHidFA","text_ar":"الاَمْرَ سَطْرًا وَاحِدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make thou the affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uniform,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one uniform thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bA^j","text_ar":"باج"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-  Also the former, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saTorN","text_ar":"سَطْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A yearling"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatuwdN","text_ar":"عَتُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", T, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of goats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaTorN","text_ar":"صَطْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. var. thereof. (IDrd, M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Msb","K","Lh","T"]},{"entry_id":"n19720","headword_ar":"سَطَرٌ","root":"sTr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n19721","headword_ar":"سُطُرٌ","root":"sTr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^usoTuwrapN","text_ar":"اُسْطُورَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}